{"tid":1009044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[印銀紙] 大陸地方債一天發行近1390億元 創單日新高","createTime":"2019-02-05T02:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T15:23:12.000Z","uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c588da7e2df0e226ad8afe2359eccf23a2ac7c2","tid":1009044,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:15:41.000Z","msg":"地方債一天發行近1390億元 創單日新高<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.finet.hk/newscenter/news_content/5c54e9cebde0b3729b591561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.finet.hk%2Fnewscenter%2Fnews_content%2F5c54e9cebde0b3729b591561&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFgKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=c1e6bfb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.finet.hk/newscenter/news_content/5c54e9cebde0b3729b591561</a><br />\n<br />\n據證券日報消息，統計數據顯示，1月31日當天，廣東省、浙江省、深圳市、内蒙古自治區、廣西壯族自治區、北京市、海南省、江蘇省8個省區市，發行地方債規模達1389.95億元，創單日發行量新高。&ensp;數據顯示，1月份地方債發行規模達4179.7億元。其中，新增債3687.6億元，借新還舊492億元。新增債中，新增一般債2276.0億元，佔提前發行一般債的39.2%;新增專項債1411.7億元，佔提前發行專項債的17.4%。"},{"pid":"a9597e67d91ef5b4774d09cc8751d1be02e7ec6c","tid":1009044,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:16:45.000Z","msg":"沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3712ebde0781fd60df407a1ccd5c5120127e2a17","tid":1009044,"uid":7206,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:27:38.000Z","msg":"地方的債務需要性愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f879effb61e9f6aa87c27bf77b24c8a539da80b0","tid":1009044,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:28:07.000Z","msg":"Rich"},{"pid":"6aef158d71c137cba789f3f6929b6805c13e9cba","tid":1009044,"uid":69484,"like":3,"dislike":22,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:28:14.000Z","msg":"其實真係冇事 <br />\n香港好多人都用經濟理論apply落中國呢個地方 <br />\n但其實唔岩駛 要知道中國係人治既 好多政策改左就得 <br />\n西方民主國家做唔到既野 中國都做到 <br />\n根本冇人敢反 所以美國好驚中國 <br />\n一個人民咁乖既國家 政權統一 集中所有資源做一樣野 <br />